<br>
Question about mezzing, when your puller is incoming with several mobs, how do you switch targets and figure out which one to mezz?<br>
<br>
I usually assist the MA to see what one he is on then 'try' to click on the other mobs to mezz.  lots of times lately it takes awhile because a) the mobs are all bunched together and i can't click them b) the melee's jump in the way c) more often than not, a combination of both.<br>
<br>
Is there a shortcut key that cycles you through the mobs in camp? i know F8 targets the closest in you LOS.  Just wondering how all you guys do it. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=lethecerulre>Lethe Cerulre</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><font color=#0066FF>Ebil Blueberry Mod </font><br>
