<br>
Most of the time it all depends on the who (group members), what you are fighting, what zone, and several other similar things.  I've done crowd control for over a dozen spiders in one pull in Velks before, really gets your adrenaline going.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"> <!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.gothictiger.net/images/letheandsuliene.gif" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><br>
