<br>
3 or 4 incoming?? AE mez them all.  Then the tank will break one and he might even move it out of the pile for you!!  Sometimes the tank will break mez and the thing will charge at you ... but then you shouldn't be that close to the pile anyway or you may mez yourself. Then simply overwrite your AE mez with a longer single target mez and you are good to go.  That makes it easy to figure out which ones you have to deal with.  Then I usually go back and slow all the mezzed ones to save my butt <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
