<br>
To figure out what to mez, I assist the MA and target what he doesn't have targeted.  If there's several, I'll use PBAoE mez or stun so that the MA can get the mob seperated from the group.  Biggest problem with this is if the critters wake up before you can get them all mezed, there is a good chance they will come after you.<br>
